@startuml
' -------------------------------------------------------
' File: sequence.puml
' -------------------------------------------------------
' Purpose   : Sequence — Error Handling Flow
' Layer     : Docs (UML)
' Author    : Mohamed Ali
' Created   : 2026-03-19
' Sprint    : 6 — Polish & Restructure
' -------------------------------------------------------

!define USE_CUSTOM_THEME
!include ../config/style.puml

title Sequence — Error Handling & Consistency (Sprint 6)

' === Header/Footer ===
header Clinic Management System - Error Handling Flow
footer Sprint 6 — Two-Layer Error Handling Strategy

' === Global Settings ===
autonumber "<b>[00]</b>"

' === Participants by Layer ===
box "Client Layer" #161B22
    actor "<color:#E6EDF3><&person></color> Client" as CLIENT
end box

box "API Layer" #0D1117
    participant "<color:#F85149><&shield></color> GlobalExceptionHandler" as EH << (M,#F85149) Middleware >>
    participant "<color:#58A6FF><&cog></color> Endpoints" as ENDP << Minimal API >>
end box

box "Core Layer" #161B22
    participant "<color:#3FB950><&cog></color> Business Service" as SVC << Service >>
    database "<color:#D29922><&hard-drive></color> DB" as DB
end box

== Scenario 1: Expected Business Error (Result Pattern) ==

CLIENT -> EH : HTTP Request
activate EH
EH -> ENDP : Forward Request
activate ENDP
ENDP -> SVC : Execute Action
activate SVC

SVC -> DB : Query Data
activate DB
DB --> SVC : Empty / Conflict
deactivate DB

note over SVC #21262D: <color:#D29922>Result Pattern</color>\nExpected errors return\nResult.Failure instead\nof throwing exceptions.

SVC --> ENDP : Result.Failure(ErrorDetails, 400/404)
deactivate SVC

note over ENDP #21262D: Endpoint maps IsFailure\nto standard JSON response.

ENDP --> EH : 400 Bad Request
deactivate ENDP
EH --> CLIENT : 400 Bad Request JSON
deactivate EH

== Scenario 2: Unexpected System Error (Exception Handling) ==

CLIENT -> EH : HTTP Request
activate EH
EH -> ENDP : Forward Request
activate ENDP
ENDP -> SVC : Execute Action
activate SVC

SVC -> DB : Query Data
activate DB
note right DB: Database timeout\nor connection loss!
DB -[#F85149]X SVC : SqlException!
deactivate DB

SVC -[#F85149]X ENDP : Unhandled Exception
deactivate SVC

ENDP -[#F85149]X EH : Unhandled Exception
deactivate ENDP

note over EH #21262D: <color:#F85149>GlobalExceptionHandler</color>\nCatches unhandled errors.\nLogs stack trace securely.\nGenerates ProblemDetails.

EH -> EH : LogError(exception)
EH --> CLIENT : 500 Internal Server Error\n(ProblemDetails JSON without stack trace)
deactivate EH

@enduml
